{"tid":418161,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"〔黑色的疤狗〕皇馬巨頭炮轟西足協:和巴薩比賽後總要談裁判","createTime":"2017-09-29T10:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T16:33:53.000Z","uid":1090,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b590a3a7964a1e3deffbd49182e2d16b602ba62d","tid":418161,"uid":1090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:23:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2017-09-29/doc-ifymmiwm0931207.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.sina.com.cn%2Fg%2Flaliga%2F2017-09-29%2Fdoc-ifymmiwm0931207.shtml&d=qSET8glXi%2FJHc%2FxYF9qUzr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=67e1c4b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/laliga/2017-09-29/doc-ifymmiwm0931207.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/20170929/ADWd-fymmiwm0929422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F20170929%2FADWd-fymmiwm0929422.jpg&h=e803e8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皇馬主席弗洛倫蒂諾一直對西班牙足協抱以不滿，近日他公開表示稱足協需要做出改變了，尤其是在裁判問題上。<br />\n<br />\n　　當今足壇，對裁判的輔助越來越多。英超、德甲、意甲等歐洲頂級聯賽都已開始引進門線技術、視頻裁判等新元素，但西甲作為歐足聯排名第一的高水平聯賽卻一直沒有引進這些技術，而在西甲賽場上一直有爭議判罰出現。<br />\n<br />\n　　皇馬主席弗洛倫蒂諾對此也有抱怨，他對西班牙足協一直有些不滿。在皇馬會員大會召開之前，他與會員們有過見面，期間就談到了聯賽問題：「西班牙足協必須改變，必須適應現代潮流。每個賽季的最後幾天都會發生異樣的事，我們必須停止這樣的勢頭，現在的狀況對西班牙足球很不利。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「在過去幾次的國家德比結束後，沒有任何談論足球本身的聲音而都在談論裁判，這很不好。我之前也只談過一次裁判的問題，現在必須給他們一些輔助了。」（斧荊）"},{"pid":"d5fb20e92dc2735c82e78731528d983a754f1176","tid":418161,"uid":18279,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"睇下人地領先你幾多分先，再望下自己幾多分，巴塞洗撚黑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1eb1b788d0212db0f55ad13394df7a1b4d1140","tid":418161,"uid":35351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 主席講得岩"},{"pid":"77ce92c0b4bba280b52e93ac58eaab0d97a9e914","tid":418161,"uid":150660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"係應該有人屌 但唔會係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b041e14bce57791553ad366f24f454ebd66ac0a5","tid":418161,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下人地領先你幾多分先，再望下自己幾多分，巴塞洗撚黑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咪就係話黑先搞到有不公，垃圾疤狗"}]}